        <label>Tau'ri</label>
        <description>Technologically savvy, diplomatically flexible, and accidentally in charge of galactic cleanup. This underfunded SGC detachment is tasked with mapping out the Dwarfgate network and keeping it out of tyrant tentacles. A huge part of their wide-spread success has been capturing and repurposing units from the Mechanoid Hive into front-line field forces.\n\nOfficial mission: survey and aid. Unofficial: beat Ba'al and the Wraith to the Archotech backdoorâ€”and try not to misdial into a star.</description>
